{"tid":1015314,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"原來而家google地圖痴線到咁!!","createTime":"2019-02-10T00:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T11:15:49.000Z","uid":119688,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0c980ecf56ff08d8bbe3ec6ec6966b65aead74eb","tid":1015314,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T00:16:15.000Z","msg":"360度圖有好耐我知<br />\n原來而家唔止街外<br />\n連室內設置都會比人影埋<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似去康民署做gym咁<br />\n都比人360度完美點相<br />\n舉個例子<br />\n蒲崗村道體育館<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/kYvBpYU5HSv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FkYvBpYU5HSv&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BP1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=9d2414f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/kYvBpYU5HSv</a><br />\n禁360度相片<br />\n<br />\n利申:我係張圖入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你咩google毒撚做gym都影<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有中間條友隻手指做咩?<br />\n咁多白頭髮好心染黑佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c2e6554f3ebad66972a27c3fbfa5baa04b3aa7","tid":1015314,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T00:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0oSEpAF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0oSEpAF.pn